author: jonl
msg: Moved converter factory to application settings.  The fact that it's stored in the session is an implementation detail that has to do with threadsafe caching of the object.  Since that's the case, made Sessiong.getConverter() package private to enable us to change this detail in the future if we really want to (unlikely, but you never know).

msg: Moved filterResponse from Application into Reponse.

msg: Created IApplicationSettings for application-wide settings.  Moved a few methods around in the settings interfaces so they are more logical.  Removed IRequiredPageSettings.
